title: Hour 1: A Controversial Putback
description:
The gang go to the KFC Bucket and Dan is very flippant with his selection. Then, the shipping container start a discussion about Thursday night's sports equinox, Billy's skepticism about prices ever going down again, and Juju Gotti apologizes fashion-based comments about other Container members.
